back, large amounts of gas\naccumulate in the central region, triggering star formation and leading to\noverly massive blue galaxies with dense stellar cores.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Sep 2018 18:00:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-24"}
