n average. The previous\nbest size lower bound was $\\Omega(n^{1+4^{-(d+1)}})$ and only held in the worst\ncase (Cheraghchi et al., JCSS 2018).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Sep 2018 23:58:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Mar 2020 22:11:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2021 17:58:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-22"}
