rm typical of weak - coupling theory, is determined\nby the bandwidth (Fermi energy). For the case of interaction with a single\noptical phonon we derive the single expression for $T_c$, valid both in\nadiabatic and antiadiabatic regimes and describing the continuous transition\nbetween these two limiting cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Sep 2018 15:19:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2018 03:32:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-08"}
